$interpreted:
Roger: You back-stabbing bastards,
where did you take Kittyeyes?
Fearful Henchman: N, none of our business. She's right there.
Roger: Koll, how dare you harm Kittyeyes! Have you gone insane!?
Kittyeyes: No, this has nothing to do with Koll...
Koll: Woo...
Kittyeyes: ... Koll, don't run away. Come back, please!
Roger: Kittyeyes, are you alright?
Kittyeyes: I'm OK; but...

Roger: You're safe, that's all that matters. 
I was so worried that you would leave me just like that...
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger, what are you...?

Roger: At first, I indeed just treated you like my little sister. 
However, my feelings towards you are gradually...
General: What happened here? A single fire should not have caused this much damage...
General: Hmm? Aren't you... Roger? Wanted criminal of the kingdom?
Roger: Damnit, the kingdom army; what terrible timing...
General: Didn't expect to net such a major target on a simple inspection. Still, for a bandit as infamous as you, why this small village?
Old Man: W, we're innocent. We were threatened by Roger and had no choice but to take them in.
Male Villager: Y, yeah. Y, you guys should take care of them, the quicker the better!
Kittyeyes: What nonsense are you people spilling!? We've been giving the village supplies all these years. How dare you people...
Roger: Kittyeyes, stop it. If that's the story they're going with, so be it...

General: I take that as confession for your crimes. If so, I'll have to take you down for the people! 
Men, get them!
Roger: Hmph, let's see if you really have what it takes to bring me down!
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger, I'll help out as well!
Roger: Is your body feeling alright?

Kittyeyes: You don't have to worry about me.
I'm more concerned about where we're gonna live afterward.
Roger: Once we get through this, let's find a place to live together in seclusion. But this time, we won't refer to each other as siblings anymore.

Kittyeyes: WHAT!?
Does that...
Roger: Look out; here they come again!

Roger: Crap, they just keep coming nonstop...
Guess I'll have to take out the leader first.
Roger: Damnit!
General: Take down the girl first!
Roger: Damnit! Stop getting in my way!
